[h3 id=Walkthroughwallsglitch
 
	" Walk through walls glitch
	$LF
]h3
[h4 id=Howto
 
	" How to
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"First, jump from near the wall and move to the wall.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Then, put two bombs in total on the place where the height of jumping becomes the highest 
	$LF
	"and the place where 1 block under the height of jumping becomes highest .
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"When bomberman enters the wall, release the left/right key . 
	$LF
]p
[h4 id=Inthewall
 
	" In the wall
	$LF
]h4
[ul 
	[li 
		" moving to left/right
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	"You can move to left/right freely even if there is no floor under Bomberman.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"But you cannot move into the right/left edge of the stage.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"If Bomberman touches the edge of the wall, it will be pushed out to the outside. 
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		"moving to up/down
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	"If Bomberman jumps when staying in the wall, it will be pushed up for 1 blocks.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"However, there is a place that cannot be done. 
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"If Bomberman jumps when it is moving, it does a usual jump.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"When Bomberman touches the ceiling after jumping in the wall, it will be pushed into the ceiling. 
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"If Bomberman stays and there is no floor (wall) under it , it will fall down.
	$LF
]p
[h4 id=Intheceiling.
 
	" In the ceiling.
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"If Bomberman jumps in the ceiling, it will warp to 16 blocks under basically.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"If Bomberman jumps when staying, it will warp to 16 blocks under but camera doesn't move.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"And if Bomberman jumps when moving, the following phenomena happen.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"1. In sideways long stage, camera will move down and game will continue normally.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"2. In vertical long stage, camera will be glitched.
	$LF
]p
